{"ja200:0.1":"Jataka ","ja200:0.2":"Dukanipata ","ja200:0.3":"Ruhakavagga ","ja200:0.4":"10. Sadhusilajataka ","ja200:1.1":"“Sariradabyam vuddhabyam, ","ja200:1.2":"sojaccam sadhusiliyam; ","ja200:1.3":"Brahmanam teva pucchama, ","ja200:1.4":"kam nu tesam vanimhase”. ","ja200:2.1":"“Attho atthi sarirasmim, ","ja200:2.2":"vuddhabyassa namo kare; ","ja200:2.3":"Attho atthi sujatasmim, ","ja200:2.4":"silam asmaka ruccati”ti. ","ja200:3.1":"Sadhusilajatakam dasamam. ","ja200:3.2":"Ruhakavaggo pancamo. ","ja200:4.1":"Tassuddanam ","ja200:5.1":"Apiruhaka rupavati musalo, ","ja200:5.2":"Pavasanti sapancamapokkharani; ","ja200:5.3":"Atha muttimavanija umhayate, ","ja200:5.4":"Ciraagata kottha sarira dasati. "}